description: A man and woman, both thought to be in their 20s, die suddenly at a house in Strathfoyle.
title: Londonderry: Man and woman in their 20s die suddenly
title_page: Londonderry: Man and woman in their 20s die suddenly - BBC News
maintext: Very sad news about the sudden deaths of a two young adults in Strathfoyle yesterday. I had received an update from the PSNI yesterday evening about the terrible situation. The investigations are continuing today. My thoughts are with the families.
